                Selectors
                |-- Selector simply represents which property corresponding to its value is going to be implemented on which specific element.

                Types of selectors : 
                    1. Element selector or Tag Selector 
                    2. Id Selector 
                    3. Class Selector 
                    4. Grouping Selector 
                    5. Descendent Selector 
                    6. Universal selector 
                    7. Advanced selector 
                        |-- Adjacent sibling selector 
                        |-- General sibling selector 
                        |-- Direct child selector 
